title: With Words and Music (1937) ROBERT ARMSTRONG

sources.title: With Words and Music (1937) ROBERT ARMSTRONG
sources.description:
Stars: Robert Armstrong, Irene Hervey, Paula Stone
Director: Andrew L. Stone

When a dime-a-dance beauty swindles a bookie out of his big bucks, he seeks revenge by duping her into backing a down-and-out Gilbert & Sullivan revival company in which she is to play a leading role. (a.k.a. The Girl Said No.)
